{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":74286,"duration_api_ms":74078,"num_turns":7,"result":"Here's the directory map for **ultrainit** — a Bash CLI tool (~CLI project type):\n\n---\n\n## Project Overview\n\nultrainit is a pure-Bash orchestrator that spawns `claude -p` subprocesses as analysis agents, collects structured JSON findings, and synthesizes them into Claude Code configuration artifacts. No frontend, no backend server — it's a pipeline tool.\n\n---\n\n## High-Priority Directories (core logic)\n\n| Directory | Role | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lib/` | Phase orchestration | 9 shell modules, one per pipeline phase; this is the heart of the tool |\n| `prompts/` | Agent system prompts | 14 markdown files fed to each `claude -p` invocation; defines agent behavior |\n| `schemas/` | Output contracts | 14 JSON Schema files; every agent's return type is defined here |\n| `scripts/` | Standalone validators | `validate-skill.sh` + `validate-subagent.sh`, run in Phase 5 and tested separately |\n| `tests/` | Test suite root | bats-core, entire test infrastructure lives here |\n| `tests/unit/` | Unit tests | 11 `.bats` files testing individual functions (budget, agent run, merge, synthesis, validation) |\n| `tests/integration/` | Integration tests | 3 phase-level tests using mock claude dispatch mode |\n| `tests/helpers/` | Test infrastructure | `mock_claude.bash` (PATH mock) + `test_helper.bash` (env setup) — critical for understanding test strategy |\n\n---\n\n## Medium-Priority Directories (supporting)\n\n| Directory | Role | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `tests/scripts/` | Validator script tests | bats tests exercising the standalone validator scripts |\n| `tests/edge/` | Edge case tests | Budget exhaustion, CLI arg parsing |\n| `tests/smoke/` | Smoke/e2e tests | Full pipeline against `tests/smoke/mini-project/` |\n| `tests/fixtures/` | All test fixtures | JSON response envelopes, findings, synthesis outputs, skill/subagent/hook examples |\n| `tests/fixtures/findings/` | Agent finding fixtures | One JSON per agent type (identity, commands, patterns, etc.) |\n| `tests/fixtures/synthesis/` | Synthesis pass fixtures | Output from both synthesis passes + merged final |\n| `test-repos/.claude/` | Example output | Complete generated config for open-webui: 30+ skills, 4 agents, 4 hooks |\n| `test-repos/.claude/skills/` | Example skills | Reference for what valid generated skills look like |\n| `test-repos/.claude/agents/` | Example agents | Reference subagent definitions |\n| `test-repos/.claude/hooks/` | Example hooks | Reference hook scripts |\n| `.github/workflows/` | CI/CD | 3 workflows: test, docker image rebuild, release/bundle |\n\n---\n\n## Low-Priority Directories (config/assets)\n\n| Directory | Role |\n|---|---|\n| `docs/` | Logo + architecture diagram assets |\n| `.claude/` | This repo's own Claude Code config |\n| `test-repos/open-webui/` | Source snapshot of open-webui (analysis target) |\n\n---\n\n**Directories warranting their own CLAUDE.md:** `lib/` (distinct phase/module conventions), `prompts/` (strict prompt engineering rules), `tests/` (mock strategy and bats conventions).","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"fa6bc86e-ba8a-4f6e-9f0a-7347f039c7de","total_cost_usd":0.27312855,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":40593,"cache_read_input_tokens":154886,"output_tokens":4961,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":40593,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":814,"cache_read_input_tokens":35069,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2866,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2866},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":8,"outputTokens":4961,"cacheReadInputTokens":154886,"cacheCreationInputTokens":40593,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.27312855,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"structured_output":{"project_type":"cli","primary_language":"TypeScript","architecture_summary":"ultrainit is a Bash CLI tool that orchestrates multiple `claude -p` subprocess invocations to analyze any codebase and generate Claude Code configuration (CLAUDE.md, skills, hooks, subagents, MCP config). The core logic lives in `lib/` (phase orchestration), `prompts/` (agent system prompts), and `schemas/` (JSON output contracts). A bats-core test suite in `tests/` uses a PATH-based mock `claude` binary to test all phases without real API calls. `test-repos/` holds a realistic example output (skills, hooks, agents for open-webui) used as validation fixtures.","directories":[{"path":"lib","role":"backend-app","priority":"high","description":"Core orchestration library: one shell module per pipeline phase (gather, ask, research, synthesize, validate, merge) plus agent spawning and utilities","estimated_file_count":9,"should_have_claude_md":true},{"path":"prompts","role":"other","priority":"high","description":"System prompt markdown files fed to each claude -p agent (identity, commands, git-forensics, patterns, synthesizer, etc.)","estimated_file_count":14,"should_have_claude_md":true},{"path":"schemas","role":"types","priority":"high","description":"JSON Schema files defining the structured output contract for every agent and synthesis pass","estimated_file_count":14,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"scripts","role":"scripts","priority":"high","description":"Standalone shell validator scripts (validate-skill.sh, validate-subagent.sh) run in Phase 5 and also exercised by the test suite","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests","role":"tests","priority":"high","description":"bats-core test suite root: all unit, integration, edge, smoke tests plus helpers and fixtures","estimated_file_count":50,"should_have_claude_md":true},{"path":"tests/unit","role":"tests","priority":"high","description":"Unit tests for individual shell functions: budget logic, agent run/skip/retry, merge, synthesis helpers, validation, utils","estimated_file_count":11,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/integration","role":"tests","priority":"high","description":"Phase-level integration tests (gather_phase, synthesize_phase, resume) using mock claude dispatch mode","estimated_file_count":3,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/scripts","role":"tests","priority":"medium","description":"bats tests specifically for the standalone scripts/validate-skill.sh and scripts/validate-subagent.sh validators","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/edge","role":"tests","priority":"medium","description":"Edge-case tests: budget exhaustion mid-run, CLI argument parsing edge cases","estimated_file_count":3,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/smoke","role":"e2e-tests","priority":"medium","description":"Smoke / end-to-end tests running the full pipeline against a minimal synthetic project","estimated_file_count":5,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/smoke/mini-project","role":"e2e-tests","priority":"medium","description":"Minimal synthetic codebase used as the target for smoke-test pipeline runs","estimated_file_count":4,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/helpers","role":"tests","priority":"high","description":"Shared bats setup helpers: tmpdir/env bootstrapping (test_helper.bash) and the PATH-based mock claude binary (mock_claude.bash)","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures","role":"tests","priority":"medium","description":"Realistic JSON fixture files representing agent outputs, used by tests instead of real claude calls","estimated_file_count":20,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/findings","role":"tests","priority":"medium","description":"Realistic per-agent finding fixtures (identity.json, commands.json, patterns.json, etc.)","estimated_file_count":12,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/synthesis","role":"tests","priority":"medium","description":"Synthesis pass output fixtures (output-docs.json, output-tooling.json, output.json)","estimated_file_count":3,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/skills","role":"tests","priority":"low","description":"Valid and invalid skill fixture directories used to test the skill validator script","estimated_file_count":4,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/subagents","role":"tests","priority":"low","description":"Subagent fixture files used to test the subagent validator script","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/hooks","role":"tests","priority":"low","description":"Hook script fixtures used to test hook validation logic","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"tests/fixtures/envelopes","role":"tests","priority":"low","description":"Mock claude response envelope JSON files matching the real claude -p --output-format json structure","estimated_file_count":3,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos","role":"other","priority":"medium","description":"Example ultrainit output: a fully generated .claude/ config for open-webui, used as a reference and for integration validation","estimated_file_count":60,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos/.claude","role":"config","priority":"medium","description":"Complete example Claude Code config directory (skills, agents, hooks, settings.json, mcp.json) generated by ultrainit for open-webui","estimated_file_count":40,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos/.claude/skills","role":"other","priority":"medium","description":"30+ example skill markdown files covering all major open-webui feature areas (add-api-client-function, add-db-migration, debug-chat-pipeline, etc.)","estimated_file_count":30,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos/.claude/agents","role":"other","priority":"medium","description":"Example subagent definitions (access-control-auditor, migration-safety-reviewer, plugin-structure-validator, chat-pipeline-analyzer)","estimated_file_count":4,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos/.claude/hooks","role":"other","priority":"medium","description":"Example hook scripts generated by ultrainit (autoformat-frontend, autoformat-python, guard-protected-files, i18n-reminder)","estimated_file_count":4,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"test-repos/open-webui","role":"other","priority":"low","description":"Snapshot of the open-webui codebase used as the analysis target for the example generated config","estimated_file_count":200,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":".github","role":"ci-cd","priority":"medium","description":"GitHub repository root (issue templates, workflows)","estimated_file_count":5,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":".github/workflows","role":"ci-cd","priority":"medium","description":"GitHub Actions workflows: test.yml (bats suite on push/PR), docker-test-image.yml (rebuild test image), release.yml (bundle and publish)","estimated_file_count":3,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":"docs","role":"documentation","priority":"low","description":"Project assets: logo.png, logo.xcf (source), diagram.png, diagram.drawio (architecture diagram source)","estimated_file_count":4,"should_have_claude_md":false},{"path":".claude","role":"config","priority":"low","description":"Claude Code settings for this repo itself (settings.json, drawio skill)","estimated_file_count":2,"should_have_claude_md":false}]},"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"c0f137cb-4146-4feb-8f7a-555472130912"}
